channel.title: Quake Expo 2016
channel.description:
Quake Expo 2016 opens tomorrow at https://qexpo2016.com. I submitted a booth for Spearmint Quake 3 (pending review).
The last Quake Expo was in 2011, which I created a [booth for Turtle Arena](https://www.quaddicted.com/webarchive/expo2011.quakewiki.net/detail-view.php%3Fid=122&category=Booths.html).
